than as a, I messed up, right?

00:00:57.970 --> 00:00:58.788
&gt;&gt; Yeah, absolutely.

00:00:58.788 --> 00:01:01.801
It can be frustrating to get stuck and
to feel like you don't know, but

00:01:01.801 --> 00:01:04.599
once you get pass that then
you've learned something.

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:06.638
And you've added a new
tool to your toolbelt.

00:01:06.638 --> 00:01:07.320
&gt;&gt; That's awesome.

00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:11.978
We've all got our own personal obstacles
or concerns when learning something new.

